h Group S.A. is a subsidiary of ARD Finance S.A.Corporate GovernanceArdagh Group S.A.’s ISS Governance QualityScore as of N/A is N/A. The pillar scores are Audit: N/A; Board: N/A; Shareholder Rights: N/A; Compensation: N/A.Corporate governance scores courtesy of Institutional Shareholder Services (ISS).  Scores indicate decile rank relative to index or region. A decile score of 1 indicates lower governance risk, while a 10 indicates higher governance risk.Yahoo Small BusinessData DisclaimerHelpSuggestionsPrivacyAbout Our AdsTerms (Updated)







Ardagh Packaging Finance PLC / Ardagh Holdings USA Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









