ardagh packaging finance plc / ardagh holdings usa inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Containers & Packaging
Sub-Industry: Containers & Packaging
Ardagh Packaging Finance PLC and Ardagh MP Holdings USA Inc. conduct business as a joint issuer of debt. The Companies Ardagh Packaging Finance PLC and Ardagh MP Holdings USA Inc. operate as a joint issuer of unsecured notes. The Companies raises funds in order to finance acquisitions and to pay related fees and expenses due to existing debt.




