Ardagh Group IPO Info


Company Name: Ardagh Group
Stock Symbol: ARD
Exchange: NYSE
Status: Priced
IPO Date: 3/15/2017
IPO Price:
19.00 (21.53%)

Underwriters
Citigroup, Deutsche Bank Securities, Goldman Sachs & Co, Barclays, Credit Suisse and J.P. Morgan
Amount of Offering: N/A
Number of Shares Offered: 16.2 Mil
Shares Outstanding After Offering: N/A
Valuation: N/A
Company Description
Ardagh Group is a global leader in metal and glass packaging solutions, producing packaging for the world's leading food, beverage and consumer brands. It operates 109 facilities in 22 countries, employing approximately 23,500 people and has global sales of approximately EUR7.7 billion.



